$interpreted: Angelia: Nigel, are you okay?
Naya: Another monster alarm!?
Naya: Come on! I'll take you all down!
Naya: Eh!? what's going on!?
Naya: Ugh! They just keep coming!
Naya: Angel? Lio?
Naya: Dammit, where are they!
Naya: Nigel?
Nigel: Dammit, dammit, dammit! Give Hyacinthus back! Give her back!
Nigel: Why... Why do you take people I care about away from me...?
Nigel: Why are you here?
Nigel: So... you saw everything?
Nigel: Hmph, funny isn't it? Want to laugh, go ahead!
Naya: I don't find it funny at all...
Naya: Holy... This is a big one!
Nigel: Damn!
Nigel: Urrgghh...
Naya: You're way too reckless. At least catch a breath!
Nigel: I can't! I have to protect the slums, or else Hyacinthus' sacrifice will have been in vain!
Nigel: What are you doing!?
Naya: Helping you, of course. You look so banged up, I just can't stand by and watch!
Nigel: I don't need your help!
Naya: You're going to get yourself killed at this rate. Hyacinthus wouldn't want to see you like this!
Naya: We might not get along, but I consider Hyacinthus my friend.
Naya: So let's just work together for once and get rid of these monsters!
Nigel: Understood. Let's go.
Naya: Why are you stopping? You injured?
Nigel: ...Thank you.
Naya: No big deal, now let's keep moving!
